°ideoir√≠ a chuireann <code>?omgf=1</code> leis an URL. D√≠chumasaigh M√≥d T√°st√°la (ag bun an leathanaigh seo) chun optamuithe a dh√©anamh infheicthe do gach duine.','%1$s wasn\'t able to process all Google Fonts on your site. %2$s'=>'N√≠ raibh %1$s in ann gach Google Fonts ar do shu√≠omh a phr√≥ise√°il. %2$s','OMGF\'s integrated Google Fonts Checker (introduced in v6) found Google Fonts implementations (added by your theme or a plugin) that cannot be automatically processed.'=>'Fuair Seice√°la√≠ Google Fonts comhth√°ite OMGF (a tugadh isteach i v6) feidhmithe Google Fonts (curtha leis ag do th√©ama n√≥ breise√°n) nach f√©idir a phr√≥ise√°il go huathoibr√≠och.','You can read <a href="%s" target="_blank">this guide</a> and attempt to fix it manually or, <a href="%s" target="_blank">upgrade to OMGF Pro</a> to fix it automatically.'=>'Is f√©idir leat <a href="%s" target="_blank">an treoir seo</a> a l√©amh agus iarracht a dh√©anamh √© a shocr√∫ de l√°imh n√≥, <a href="%s" target="_blank">uasghr√°d√∫ a dh√©anamh go OMGF Pro</a> chun √© a shocr√∫ go huathoibr√≠och.','Some (or all) of the entries listed here might coincide with the list of potential issues listed below in the yellow box. Fix them first and visit the links below, to refresh these results. In some cases, an <a href="%s" target="_blank">upgrade to OMGF Pro</a> might be required.'=>'D\'fh√©adfadh cuid de na hiontr√°lacha (n√≥ gach ceann acu) at√° liostaithe anseo teacht salach ar an liosta d\'fhadhbanna f√©ideartha at√° liostaithe th√≠os sa bhosca bu√≠. Socraigh iad sin ar dt√∫s agus tabhair cuairt ar na naisc th√≠os, chun na tortha√≠ seo a athnuachan. I gc√°sanna √°irithe, d\'fh√©adfadh go mbeadh <a href="%s" target="_blank">uasghr√°d√∫ go OMGF Pro</a> ag teast√°il.','was found on:'=>'fuarthas ar:','This list is limited to 5 pages, because most entries will most likely be duplicates.'=>'T√° an liosta seo teoranta do 5 leathanach, mar is d√≥cha gur d√∫bailt√≠ a bheidh i bhformh√≥r na n-iontr√°lacha.','Let\'s