span class="omgf-cache-legend-item-title">Aimsithe</span> T√° st√≠lbhileog ann ar do ch√≥ras comhad.','<span class="omgf-cache-legend-item-title">Unloaded</span> Stylesheet exists but is not loaded in the frontend.'=>'<span class="omgf-cache-legend-item-title">D√≠luchtaithe</span> T√° st√≠lbhileog ann ach n√≠l s√≠ luchtaithe sa chomh√©adan.','<span class="omgf-cache-legend-item-title">Stale</span> Settings were changed and the stylesheet\'s content does not reflect those changes.'=>'<span class="omgf-cache-legend-item-title">Seanchaite</span> Athra√≠odh socruithe agus n√≠ l√©ir√≠onn √°bhar na st√≠lbhileoige na hathruithe sin.','<span class=\'omgf-cache-legend-item-title\'>Pending / Not Found</span> Any changes you made to this stylesheet will be processed the next time the page it was found on is requested. If you didn\'t make any changes, it\'s probably orphaned and it\'s safe to remove it.'=>'<span class=\'omgf-cache-legend-item-title\'>Ar Feitheamh / N√≠or Aims√≠odh</span> D√©anfar aon athruithe a rinne t√∫ ar an st√≠lbhileog seo a phr√≥ise√°il an ch√©ad uair eile a iarrfar an leathanach ar a bhfuarthas √≠. Mura ndearna t√∫ aon athruithe, is d√≥cha go bhfuil s√≠ d√≠lleachta agus t√° s√© s√°bh√°ilte √≠ a bhaint.','Save & Optimize'=>'S√°bh√°il & Optamaigh','You\'re not cool enough to access this page.'=>'N√≠l sibh fionnuar go leor chun rochtain a fh√°il ar an leathanach seo.','OMGF | Optimize My Google Fonts'=>'OMGF | Optamaigh Mo Google Fonts','Local Fonts'=>'Cl√≥nna √°iti√∫la','Advanced'=>'Ard-','Help'=>'Cabhair','Coded with %s in The Netherlands @ <strong>Daan.dev</strong>.'=>'C√≥daithe le %s san √çsilt√≠r @ <strong>Daan.dev</strong>.','Recently tagged <a target="_blank" href="%s"><strong>#OMGF</strong></a> on my blog:'=>'Le d√©ana√≠ clib√°ilte <a target="_blank" href="%s"><strong>#OMGF</strong></a> ar mo bhlag:','Fonts Cache Directory'=>'Eolaire taisce cl√≥nna','Downloaded stylesheets and font files %1$s are stored in: <code>%2$s</code>.'=>'St√≠lbhileoga √≠osl√≥d√°ilte agus comhaid cl√≥nna %1$s st√≥r√°ilte i: <code>%2$s</code>.','(for this site)'=>'(don su√≠omh seo)','White-label Stylesheets (Pro)'=>'St√≠lbhileoga lip√©ad b√°n (pro)','Enable this option to remove all branding and comments from generated stylesheets, further decreasing their size. %s'=>'Cumasaigh an rogha seo chun gach brand√°il agus tr√°cht a bhaint as st√≠lbhileoga ginte, ag laghd√∫ a m√©id tuilleadh. %s','Enable this option (on all instances) if you\'re planning to use %s in a (variation of a) Development > Testing > Acceptance/Staging > Production workflow. %s'=>'Cumasaigh an rogha seo (ar gach c√°s) m√° t√° s√© beartaithe agat %s a √∫s√°id i (leagan de) sreabhadh oibre Forbartha > T√°st√°la > Glactha/St√°itse > T√°irgeachta. %s','Developer Mode (Pro)'=>'M√≥d forbr√≥ra (pro)','This option is disabled, because <strong>Developer Mode (Pro)</strong> is enabled.'=>'T√° an rogha seo d√≠chumasaithe, toisc go bhfuil <strong>M√≥d Forbr√≥ra (Pro)</strong> cumasaithe.','Modify the <code>src</code> attribute for font files and stylesheets generated by OMGF Pro. This can be anything; from an absolute URL pointing to your CDN (e.g. <code>%s</code>) to an alternate relative URL (e.g. <code>/renamed-wp-content-dir/alternate/path/to/font-files</code>) to work with <em>security thru obscurity</em> plugins. Enter the full path to OMGF\'s files. Default: (empty) %s'=>'Athraigh an tr√©ith <code>src</code> do chomhaid cl√≥nna agus st√≠lbhileoga a ghineann OMGF Pro. Is f√©idir √© seo a bheith ar bith; √≥ URL absal√≥ideach ag d√≠ri√∫ ar do CDN (e.g. <code>%s</code>) go URL coibhneasta malartach (e.g. <code>/renamed-wp-content-dir/alternate/path/to/font-files</code>) chun oibri√∫ le breise√°in <em>sl√°nd√°la tr√≠ doil√©ire</em>. Cuir isteach an cos√°n ioml√°n chuig comhaid OMGF. R√©amhshocr√∫: (folamh) %s','Modify Source URL (Pro)'=>'Athraigh URL foinse (pro)','e.g. https://cdn.mydomain.com/alternate/relative-path'=>'e.g. https://cdn.mydomain.com/alternate/relative-path','Legacy Browser Compatibility'=>'Comhoiri√∫nacht brabhs√°la√≠ oidhreachta','Enable this option to use an older (Windows 7) User-Agent to add support for legacy browsers. Enabling this option negatively impacts file compression and disables Variable Fonts support. Default: off.'=>'Cumasaigh an rogha seo chun sean-Ghn√≠omhaire √ös√°ideora (Windows 7) a √∫s√°id chun taca√≠ocht a chur le brabhs√°laithe oidhreachta. B√≠onn tionchar di√∫ltach ag cumas√∫ na rogha seo ar chomhbhr√∫ comhad agus d√≠chumasa√≠onn s√© taca√≠ocht Cl√≥nna Athraitheacha. R√©amhshocr√∫: as.','Divi Compatibility'=>'Comhoiri√∫nacht Divi','Divi uses the same handle for Google Fonts stylesheets with different configurations. OMGF includes compatibility fixes to make sure these different stylesheets are processed correctly. Enable this if you see some fonts not appearing correctly. Default: off'=>'√ös√°ideann Divi an l√°imhse√°il ch√©anna do st√≠lbhileoga Google Fonts le cumra√≠ochta√≠ √©ags√∫la. Cuims√≠onn OMGF r√©itigh chomhoiri√∫nachta chun a chinnti√∫ go bpr√≥ise√°iltear na st√≠lbhileoga √©ags√∫la seo i gceart. Cumasaigh √© seo m√° fheiceann t√∫ roinnt cl√≥nna nach bhfuil ag teacht chun cinn i gceart. R√©amhshocr√∫: as','Auto-Configure Subsets'=>'Fo-thacair a chumr√∫ go huathoibr√≠och','When this option is checked, %s will set the <strong>Used Subset(s)</strong> option to only use subsets that\'re available for <u>all</u> detected font families. Novice users are advised to leave this enabled.'=>'Nuair a bheidh an rogha seo seice√°ilte, socr√≥idh %s an rogha <strong>Fo-thacar(√≠) √ös√°idte</strong> chun fo-thacair at√° ar f√°il do <u>gach</u> teaghlach cl√≥nna braite amh√°in a √∫s√°id. Moltar d\'√∫s√°ideoir√≠ nua √© seo a fh√°g√°il cumasaithe.','Used Subset(s)'=>'Fo-thacar(√≠) √∫s√°idte','Any changes made to this setting will be overwritten, because <strong>Auto-configure Subsets</strong> is enabled. Disable it if you wish to manage <strong>Used Subset(s)</strong> yourself. <u>Novice users shouldn\'t change this setting</u>!'=>'D√©anfar aon athruithe a dh√©antar ar an socr√∫ seo a fhorscr√≠obh, toisc go bhfuil <strong>Fo-thacair a chumr√∫ go huathoibr√≠och</strong> cumasaithe. D√≠chumasaigh √© m√°s mian leat <strong>Fo-thacar(√≠) √ös√°idte</strong> a bhainisti√∫ t√∫ f√©in. <u>N√≠or cheart d\'√∫s√°ideoir√≠ nua an socr√∫ seo a athr√∫</u>!','A subset is a (limited) set of characters belonging to an alphabet. Default: <code>latin</code>, <code>latin-ext</code>. Limit the selection to subsets your site actually uses. Selecting <u>too many</u> subsets can negatively impact performance! <em>Latin Extended and Vietnamese are an add-ons for Latin and can\'t be used by itself. Use CTRL + click to select multiple values.</em>'=>'Is tacar (teoranta) carachtar √© fo-thacar a bhaineann le haib√≠tir. R√©amhshocr√∫: <code>latin</code>, <code>latin-ext</code>. Teorannaigh an rogha do na fo-thacair a √∫s√°ideann do shu√≠omh i nd√°ir√≠re. Is f√©idir le roghn√∫ <u>r√≥-mh√≥r</u> fo-thacair tionchar di√∫ltach a imirt ar fheidhm√≠ocht! <em>Is breise√°in iad Latin Extended agus V√≠tneaimis do Latin agus n√≠ f√©idir iad a √∫s√°id leo f√©in. √ös√°id CTRL + clice√°il chun il-luachanna a roghn√∫.</em>','This disables the %s admin bar menu item and stops the Google Fonts checker from running in the frontend.'=>'D√≠chumasa√≠onn s√© seo an mh√≠r roghchl√°ir barra riarach√°in %s agus cuireann s√© stop le seice√°la√≠ Google Fonts √≥ rith sa chomh√©adan.','This setting will resume functioning once the Google Fonts checker has finished running.'=>'Leanfaidh an socr√∫ seo ag feidhmi√∫ nuair a bheidh an seice√°la√≠ Google Fonts cr√≠ochnaithe ag rith.','Disable Admin Bar Menu'=>'D√≠chumasaigh roghchl√°r an bharra riarach√°in','Debug Mode'=>'M√≥d d√≠fhabhtaithe','Don\'t enable this option, unless when asked by me (Daan) or, if you know what you\'re doing.'=>'N√° cumasaigh an rogha seo, ach amh√°in m√° iarrann mise (Daan) ort √©, n√≥ m√° t√° a fhios agat cad at√° √° dh√©anamh agat.','Download Log'=>'√çosl